*   ## **_ORANGE CASSIDY AND FTR DEF. RUSH, RODERICK STRONG AND BEAST MUERTO_**
    

Orange Cassidy gives RUSH an Orange Punch to absolutely no effect before FTR jump on and allow OC to hit a second Orange Punch combined with a shatter machine for the win.

After the match, the Acclaimed come out to disrespect FTR but they had their mics shut off. Dad says he's not much for words anyway and the Acclaimed fight with FTR until security pulls them apart.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b471b00e-8a29-48f5-9be1-61adf51a1288/20240807_183808.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_KAMILLE PINS 2 LOCAL TALENT AT ONCE_**
    

After the match, Mercedes is clowning Britt Baker for being suspended by the Elite. Tony Shiavonne announces that Tony Khan has overruled the Elite and brought Britt Baker back to TV.

Britt Baker appears "via satellite" to say she's going to be the first in AEW to pin Mercedes

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1048a811-7545-4360-8309-83dd4d375ac4/20240807_190839.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_BRYAN DANIELSON DEF. JEFF JARRETT IN AN ANYTHING GOES MATCH_**
    

Bryan and Jarrett go to war in a wild brawl that ends with Bryan hitting Jarrett with a chair assisted Busaiku Flying Knee

After the match Swerve comes out to tell Bryan that if Jarrett could take him to the limit like this then wait until he sees what Swerve does at All In.

Swerve says he wants to test himself the way Bryan did tonight. So next week Swerve will face Yuta

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dce05ca3-960d-4f79-a2da-c84133591bca/20240807_190903.jpg?format=original)